@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_choqza(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.29 - v1 + 0.78)) / 0.58)
    v1 = (tmp / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.85) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.89)))
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.16 * v0 + 0.81) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.10)))
    v0 = (0.68 + 0.61)
    data[tid] = v0
